{"calories":"1000","carbs":73,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"\u003cp\u003eWe’ve partnered with Food52, an online community of home cooks and recipe writers, to bring you their most memorable recipes for sharing with friends and family. Their test kitchen chef Josh Cohen wants to break home cooks out of their “broccoli comfort zone” and go beyond steaming or sautéing. In this recipe, he roasts and blends the broccoli with pine nuts and Parmesan for a seasonal twist on classic pesto. Tossed with mini penne and baked under a blanket of fresh mozzarella, this ooey, gooey pasta dish is broccoli like you’ve never had before. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eRecipe adapted from Food52.","difficulty":"easy","external_id":"59e6cb3eee","fat":66,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/57462/large_cropped_Azw4HNxQQaPmGpLEh6Q0_Broccoli_Pesto_Penne_with_Fresh_Mozzarella_and_Smoked_Salt___THUMB.jpg","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/57460/5nMJqfIZSnu84ZLiwixA_Broccoli_Pesto_Penne_with_Fresh_Mozzarella_and_Smoked_Salt___MOBILE.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/57461/2D14NArERTCsrOAs3S7d_Broccoli_Pesto_Penne_with_Fresh_Mozzarella_and_Smoked_Salt___THUMB.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/57461/menu_small_2D14NArERTCsrOAs3S7d_Broccoli_Pesto_Penne_with_Fresh_Mozzarella_and_Smoked_Salt___THUMB.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/57459/4LPTaL9CS6Glv8ITsGGQ_Broccoli_Pesto_Penne_with_Fresh_Mozzarella_and_Smoked_Salt___HERO.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/57459/hero_4LPTaL9CS6Glv8ITsGGQ_Broccoli_Pesto_Penne_with_Fresh_Mozzarella_and_Smoked_Salt___HERO.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/57459/menu_small_4LPTaL9CS6Glv8ITsGGQ_Broccoli_Pesto_Penne_with_Fresh_Mozzarella_and_Smoked_Salt___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/57459/small_square_4LPTaL9CS6Glv8ITsGGQ_Broccoli_Pesto_Penne_with_Fresh_Mozzarella_and_Smoked_Salt___HERO.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/57459/medium_square_4LPTaL9CS6Glv8ITsGGQ_Broccoli_Pesto_Penne_with_Fresh_Mozzarella_and_Smoked_Salt___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/57459/recipe_profile_page_4LPTaL9CS6Glv8ITsGGQ_Broccoli_Pesto_Penne_with_Fresh_Mozzarella_and_Smoked_Salt___HERO.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}}],"name":"Broccoli Pesto Penne with Fresh Mozzarella and Smoked Salt","novice_time":null,"portion_count":2,"prep_time":"30-40","pro_time":null,"product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":30,"public_slug":"broccoli-pesto-penne-with-fresh-mozzarella-and-smoked-salt-2","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/39597/recipe_card20181207-10-rdk9al.pdf","recipe_id":5874,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Broccoli Pesto Penne","subtitle":"with Fresh Mozzarella and Smoked Salt","title":"Broccoli Pesto Penne","legal_copy_short":"Recipe adapted from Food52.","available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"\u003cp\u003eBe sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us—you\u0026#x27;ll be glad you did!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eThin slices of mozzarella will allow for more coverage of the pasta as it bakes in Step 5. Don\u0026#x27;t worry if the slices aren\u0026#x27;t perfect—they\u0026#x27;ll melt in the oven. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you don\u0026#x27;t have a blender or food processor, finely chop roasted broccoli, garlic clove, and pine nuts, then combine in a bowl with remaining pesto ingredients. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eUse the remaining mascarpone as a spread for toast or a dip for fresh fruit. \u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["8\" medium pot","baking sheet","blender or food processor (optional)"],"id":5874,"ingredients":["broccoli florets","lemon","fresh mozzarella","garlic","mini penne pasta","pine nuts","grated Parmesan cheese","mascarpone cheese","smoked sea salt","aluminum tin"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"broccoli florets","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2027/medium_square_BROCCOLI_FLORETS_-4468_copy.jpg"},{"name":"lemon","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/16/medium_square_LEMON_SLICED_1_copy.jpg"},{"name":"fresh mozzarella","quantity":"4.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1093/medium_square_fresh_mozzarella.jpg"},{"name":"garlic","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"clove","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2/medium_square_GARLIC_PEELED_copy.jpg"},{"name":"mini penne pasta","quantity":"6.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2363/medium_square_penne-pasta_copy.jpg"},{"name":"pine nuts","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/111/medium_square_pine-nuts-board.jpg"},{"name":"grated Parmesan cheese","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2308/medium_square_PARM_copy.jpg"},{"name":"mascarpone cheese","quantity":"4.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1501/medium_square_MASCARPONE_CHEESE_copy.jpg"},{"name":"smoked sea salt","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"teaspoon","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1086/medium_square_maldon_smoked.jpg"},{"name":"aluminum tin","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/830/medium_square_square_baking_tin.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["olive oil","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"olive oil","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":null,"displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/267/medium_square_olive-oil-test.jpg"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":12,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":13,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/57569/recipe_card_size_JyYOLPpQD6qNcwmIo7wR_1._Prepare_Ingredients.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003ePreheat oven to 450°F. Bring a medium pot of water to a boil over high heat. Rinse all produce. Roughly chop \u003cstrong\u003ebroccoli\u003c/strong\u003e. If you have a zester and want to add even more lemon flavor to your pesto, zest \u003cstrong\u003eup to .5\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003elemon\u003c/strong\u003e, then halve. Thinly slice \u003cstrong\u003emozzarella \u003c/strong\u003e(see recipe tip). Roughly chop \u003cstrong\u003egarlic\u003c/strong\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Roast broccoli","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/57570/recipe_card_size_p1KJyYnPToWGBHS6OXWh_2._Roast_Broccoliu.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eOn a baking sheet, toss \u003cstrong\u003ebroccoli\u003c/strong\u003e with \u003cstrong\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.5 teaspoon kosher salt\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired. Arrange in a single layer and roast until beginning to brown, 7-9 minutes.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Cook mini penne","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/57571/recipe_card_size_px3RtZPCQoinviWQrf3Z_3._Cook_Penne.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile broccoli roasts, season boiling water generously with \u003cstrong\u003ekosher\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003emini\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003epenne\u003c/strong\u003e and cook until al dente, about 7 minutes. Drain and return to pot, off heat.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Make broccoli pesto","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/57572/recipe_card_size_51jEkCQrQW7luFy0OgX0_4._Make_Broccoli_Pesto.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile pasta cooks, in a blender or food processor, combine \u003cstrong\u003epine nuts\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003egarlic\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003elemon zest\u003c/strong\u003e (if using), \u003cstrong\u003ejuice of .5 lemon\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of roasted broccoli\u003c/strong\u003e. Pulse until just combined (see recipe tip). With motor running, stream in \u003cstrong\u003e.25 cup olive oil \u003c/strong\u003euntil smooth. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003eParmesan\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon kosher salt\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Bake broccoli pesto penne","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/57573/recipe_card_size_vCVyca7yT6ekPjw3fRfK_5._Bake_Broccoli_Pesto_Penne_2X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eAdd \u003cstrong\u003ebroccoli pesto\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of mascarpone\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003eremaining roasted broccoli\u003c/strong\u003e to pot with penne, still off heat, and stir to combine (see recipe tip). Wipe baking sheet clean and add \u003cstrong\u003ealuminum\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003etin\u003c/strong\u003e, reshaping if bent. Transfer \u003cstrong\u003ebroccoli pesto\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003epenne\u003c/strong\u003e to \u003cstrong\u003etin\u003c/strong\u003e and spread in an even layer. Top evenly with \u003cstrong\u003emozzarella slices\u003c/strong\u003e, then sprinkle over \u003cstrong\u003esmoked sea salt \u003c/strong\u003e(feel free to use less, if desired). Bake until cheese is melted, 3-5 minutes.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Plate broccoli pesto penne","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/57574/recipe_card_size_ij1Yf1puQhaMoj0qRjl5_6._Plate_Pesto.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eOnce baked, let \u003cstrong\u003ebroccoli pesto penne\u003c/strong\u003e cool about 5 minutes (this is a great time to set the table or get ahead on dishes). Divide between serving bowls and dig in!\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"food52","slug":"food52","hex_color":"#2d4558"}],"allergens":[{"name":"Milk","slug":"milk","hex_color":""},{"name":"Tree Nuts","slug":"tree nuts","hex_color":""},{"name":"Wheat","slug":"wheat","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Pasta","slug":"pasta","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"food52","slug":"food52","hex_color":"#2d4558"}],"feature":[{"name":"food52","slug":"food52","hex_color":"#2d4558"}]}}